title: Eagles parade had 'more people than the Trump inauguration': Philly mayor
text:
Eagles parade had 'more people than the Trump inauguration': Philly mayor Friday, February 09, 2018 - 00:54 
Philadelphia mayor Jim Kenney joked on Friday that the Eagles parade, which was estimated to have attracted about two million fans, had 'more people than the Trump inauguration'. Rough Cut (no reporter narration).
